WEBVTT

00:01:28.676 --> 00:01:31.020
I may get many sponsors, a lot of money,

00:01:31.044 --> 00:01:33.830
tons of interviews,
and be on TV!" I thought.

00:01:33.854 --> 00:01:35.576
(Laughter)

00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:38.820
But after coming back to Japan,

00:01:38.844 --> 00:01:41.848
totally nothing changed in my life.

00:01:41.872 --> 00:01:43.474
(Laughter)

00:01:43.607 --> 00:01:46.843
I realized society
didn't value my passion.

00:01:48.168 --> 00:01:50.712
So I went back to my college

00:01:50.736 --> 00:01:53.843
and became a typical Japanese worker
as a systems engineer.

00:01:55.244 --> 00:02:00.851
I felt my passion,
heart and soul, had left my body.